projects.projDesc: An A.I. driven detection system to collect water parameters. Using image detection AI a unit gathers images and classifies objects detected in a body of water. This data is then processed and displayed for the customer on a front end application.

An exploration of modular theatre to explore the concept of immersive theatre. Using javascript and a found algorithm to process green screen this is a proof of concept on how the audience can fully take control of the media and make every viewing of the same media unique.
